metadata.query: Hugging Face models for text generation

sparql_query:
PREFIX daimo: <http://purl.org/pionera/daimo#>

PREFIX odrl: <http://www.w3.org/ns/odrl/2/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?model WHERE {
 ?model rdf:type daimo:Model ;
 odrl:hasPolicy ?policy .
 ?policy dcterms:identifier ?license .
 # License filter moved to WHERE clause
}
LIMIT 10

metadata.query: How many models are in the catalog?

sparql_query:
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX daimo: <http://purl.org/pionera/daimo#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> SELECT ?library (COUNT(?model) AS )
WHERE { ?model a daimo:Model ; daimo:library ?library .
}
GROUP BY ?library
ORDER BY DESC( )

sparql_query:
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX daimo: <http://purl.org/pionera/daimo#> PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
SELECT ?source (COUNT(?model) AS ) (AVG(?downloads) AS ) (MAX(?downloads) AS ) (MIN(?downloads) AS )
WHERE { ?model a daimo:Model ; dcterms:source ?source . OPTIONAL { ?model daimo:downloads ?downloads } FILTER(BOUND(?downloads))
}
GROUP BY ?source
ORDER BY DESC( )

sparql_query:
PREFIX dcterms: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
